Title: Part 6: The Brown Wizard
Text:
After we got new horses and provisions,
we can now start the journey to the forest gate!
CompleteText:
There it is... the forest gate of the Elves to Mirkwood or also called the Greenwood...

At least it used to be... now the forest is partially cursed and an evil magic seems to be strong! Rumors says if you leave the path you get lost forever!

Who is standing there, another wizard? And are these rabbits pulling him on a sleigh?
